name: Pametnik u shumenu, kubrat 2 od 6 colourized remix
description: Part of a series of drawings from scottx.tez (@spike_0124, https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/scott/creations) , the Monument to 1300 Years of Bulgarian History, location in Shumen Bulgaria. The cubist monument sits on top of a hill located in Shumen, and depicts the kings of Bulgaria, pictured here is kubrat. This piece is a three-way collab, illustration by scott, the colourized version by  blissofart.tez (@blissofart on twitter), and animated remix by @TBinkiewinkie
